Package com.att.android.arodatacollector.activities

Contains classes that represent the ARO Data Collector user interface.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AROCollectorCompletedActivity
    Represents the Trace Completed screen of the ARO Data Collector, which displays a summary of trace collection details.
    AROCollectorHomeActivity
    Represents the Home screen of the ARO Data Collector, which contains butttons that allow the user to hide or stop the application.
    AROCollectorLegalTermsActivity
    Represents the Legal Terms screen of the ARO Data Collector.
    AROCollectorMainActivity
    Represents the Landing screen, which is the main UI screen of the ARO Data Collector.
    AROCollectorSplashActivity
    Represents the Splash screen, which is the first UI screen that appears when the ARO Data Collector is launched and the application data is being initialized.
    AROCollectorTaskManagerActivity
    Represents the Task Killer screen of the ARO Data Collector, which lists all of the running processes and provides an option to select and cancel those processes.

Package com.att.android.arodatacollector.activities Description

Contains classes that represent the ARO Data Collector user interface.

All of the UI classes in this package respond to user activity.
